# {{senseid|en|Q703}}A soft, waxy, silvery reactive [[metal]] that is never found unbound in nature; an element (''symbol'' K) with an [[atomic number]] of 19 and [[atomic weight]] of 39.0983. The symbol is derived from the Latin ''[[kalium]]''.
# {{lb|en|countable}} A single [[atom]] of this element.

